es.%20As%20working%20mothers%2C%20moments%20of%20guilt%20are%20inevitable.%20I%20lean%20on%20my%20staff%20and%20my%20loved%20ones%20for%20support.%20I%20aim%20to%20balance%20my%20personal%20and%20professional%20life%20because%20caring%20for%20myself%20benefits%20my%20child%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpening%20up%20about%20her%20decision%20to%20freeze%20her%20eggs%2C%20Upasana%20Kamineni%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20froze%20my%20eggs%20because%20every%20woman%20deserves%20the%20autonomy%20to%20make%20decisions%20about%20motherhood%20based%20on%20their%20desires%20and%20timelines.%20It%20was%20a%20personal%20journey%20that%20I%20embraced%20on%20my%20own.%20Why%20should%20anything%20practical%20or%20enhancing%20life's%20comfort%20be%20taboo.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20unversed%2C%20Ram%20Charan%20and%20Upasana%20Kamineni%20got%20married%20in%20June%202012%20and%20welcomed%20Klin%20Kaara%20On%20June%2020%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715664660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fsnpnnma_ram-charan_625x300_14_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fupasana-on-how-ram-charan-helped-her-battle-postpartum-depression-he-moved-into-my-parents-place-5659067%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ram%20Charan%20and%20Upasana%20Kamineni%20welcomed%20Klin%20Kaara%20in%20June%202023%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fupasana-on-how-ram-charan-helped-her-battle-postpartum-depression-he-moved-into-my-parents-place-5659067%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fupasana-on-how-ram-charan-helped-her-battle-postpartum-depression-he-moved-into-my-parents-place-5659067%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fupasana-on-how-ram-charan-helped-her-battle-postpartum-depression-he-moved-into-my