ith%20a%20core%20reservist%20call-up%20of%2038%2C000%20more%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEstonia%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bseriously%26quot%3B%20discussing%20sending%20troops%20to%20Ukraine%20in%20roles%20positioned%20away%20from%20the%20front%20lines%2C%20per%20a%20national%20security%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMadis%20Roll%2C%20national%20security%20advisor%20to%20Estonia's%20president%2C%20told%20military%20news%20outlet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbreakingdefense.com%2F2024%2F05%2Festonia-seriously-discussing-sending-troops-to-rear-jobs-in-ukraine-official%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBreaking%20Defense%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20his%20country's%20leaders%20were%20assessing%20the%20viability%20of%20sending%20Estonian%20soldiers%20to%20%26quot%3Brear%26quot%3B%20roles%20that%20wouldn't%20see%20direct%20combat%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20move%20would%20help%20relieve%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-manpower-problem-could-get-worse-before-it-gets-better-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUkraine's%20manpower%20crunch%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20allow%20it%20to%20send%20more%20soldiers%20to%20the%20front%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20Estonia%2C%20a%20North%20Atlantic%20Treaty%20Organization%20country%2C%20prefers%20to%20act%20together%20with%20the%20alliance's%20major%20members%2C%20it's%20also%20not%20closed%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20jumping%20in%20with%20a%20smaller%20group%20of%20allies%2C%20Roll%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDiscussions%20are%20ongoing%2C%26quot%3B%20Roll%20told%20Breaking%20Defense.%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20be%20looking%20at%20all%20the%20possibilities.%20We%20shouldn't%20have%20our%20minds%20restricted%20as%20to%20what%20we%20can%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBreaking%20Defense%20reported%20that%20Roll%20made%20these%20comments%20on%20Friday%2C%20just%20days%20after%20the%20country's%20defense%20chief%2C%20Gen.%20Martin%20Herem%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbreakingdefense.com%2F2024%2F05%2Festonia-had-discussed-sending-non-front-line-troops-to-ukraine-general%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20outlet%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Estonia%20had%20internally%20talked%20about%20sending%20troops%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20hadn't%20been%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%20discussion%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20domestic%20political%20concerns%2C%20Herem%20told%20the%20military%20news%20site%20on%20May%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEstonia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20geographically%20closest%20NATO%20members%20to%20Russia%2C%20with%20an%20eastern%20border%20shared%20with%20the%20Russian%20regions%20Pskov%20and%20Leningrad.%20Its%20military%20relies%20largely%20on%20reservist%20units%2C%20with%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmil.ee%2Fen%2Fdefence-forces%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E4%2C200%20permanent%20staff%20and%2038%2C000%20reserve%20troops%3C%2Fa%3E%20ready%20for%20wartime%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditional%20reserves%20bring%20the%20total%20number%20of%20Estonians%20with%20military%20training%20to%20around%20230%2C000%20of%20its%201.3%20million%20population%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmil.ee%2Fen%2Fdefence-forces%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eofficial%20defense%20forces%20website.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d36c073-4833-4db1-919c-e76f3155e1ef%5C%22%3EMore%20NATO%20members%20are%20thinking%20about%20troops%20in%20Ukraine%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETallinn%20is%20now%20joining%20a%20growing%20chorus%20of%20alliance%20members%20touting%20the%20possibility%20of%20backing%20Ukraine's%20forces%20with%20troops%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-emmanual-macron-france-join-ukraine-war-on-russia-conditions-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFrench%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%3C%2Fa%3E%20drawing%20Moscow's%20ire%20for%20repeatedly%20floating%20such%20a%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Balt