n%20India's%20Chabahar%20Pact%20With%20Iran%2C%20A%20US%20Warning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20India%20signed%20a%2010-year%20contract%20to%20operate%20Iran's%20Chabahar%20port%2C%20the%20US%20has%20warned%20that%20its%20sanctions%20on%20Tehran%20remain%20in%20place%20and%20anyone%20considering%20business%20deals%20with%20them%20needs%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Baware%20of%20the%20potential%20risk%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20yesterday%20signed%20the%20contract%20to%20operate%20Chabahar%20port%20to%20expand%20trade%20with%20Central%20Asia.%20The%20port%20on%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Oman%20will%20provide%20Indian%20goods%20a%20gateway%20to%20reach%20landlocked%20Afghanistan%20and%20Central%20Asia%20using%20a%20road%20and%20rail%20project%20called%20International%20North-South%20Transport%20Corridor.%20This%20route%20bypasses%20Pakistan.%20India%20had%20first%20proposed%20this%20plan%20back%20in%202003%2C%20but%20US%20sanctions%20on%20Iran%20over%20its%20suspected%20nuclear%20programme%20slowed%20down%20the%20port's%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20India's%20pact%20with%20Iran%2C%20deputy%20spokesperson%20of%20US%20Department%20of%20State%20Vedant%20Patel%20told%20the%20media%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20aware%20of%20these%20reports%20that%20Iran%20and%20India%20have%20signed%20a%20deal%20concerning%20the%20Chabahar%20port.%20I%20will%20let%20the%20government%20of%20India%20speak%20to%20its%20own%20foreign%20policy%20goals%20vis-a-vis%20the%20Chabahar%20port%20as%20well%20as%20its%20own%20bilateral%20relationship%20with%20Iran.%20I%20will%20just%20say%2C%20as%20it%20relates%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20US%20sanctions%20on%20Iran%20remain%20in%20place%20and%20we%20will%20continue%20to%20enforce%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Banyone%20considering%20business%20deals%20with%20Iran%2C%20they%20need%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20the%20potential%20risk%20that%20they%20are%20opening%20themselves%20up%20to%20and%20the%20potential%20risk%20of%20sanctions%26quot%3B.%20When%20a%20reporter%20asked%20if%20there's%20any%20exemption%20for%20this%2C%20Mr%20Patel%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BNo%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20Port%20Plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20long-term%20agreement%20to%20develop%20the%20Chabahar%20port%20was%20signed%20by%20Indian%20Ports%20Global%20Limited%20and%20the%20Port%20and%20Maritime%20Organisation%20of%20Iran%2C%20an%20official%20statement%20has%20said.%20IPGL%20will%20invest%20about%20%24120%20million%20and%20another%20%24250%20million%20will%20be%20raised%20as%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceremony%20for%20the%C2%A0signing%20of%20the%20pact%20was%20signed%20was%20attended%20by%20Sarbananda%20Sonowal%2C%20Union%20Minister%20for%20Ports%2C%20Shipping%20and%20Waterways%2C%20and%20Iran's%20Transport%20and%20Urban%20Development%20Minister%20Mehrdad%20Bazrpash%20in%20Tehran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20pact%20replaces%20a%202016%20agreement%2C%20which%20covered%20India's%20operations%20at%20Shahid%20Beheshti%20terminal%20in%20Chabahar%20port%20and%20was%20renewed%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20India%20takes%20over%20the%20management%20of%20an%20overseas%20port%20that%20is%20expected%20to%20boost%20exponentially%20trade%20among%20India%2C%20Iran%20and%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20allocated%20Rs%20100%20crore%20for%20the%20Chabahar%20Port%20for%202024-25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%2010%20years%20long%20term%20lease%20agreement%20further%20strengthens%20the%20bilateral%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20while%20bolstering%20confidence%20and%20boosting%20trust%20of%20trading%20communities%20from%20the%20region%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20the%20signature%20of%20this%20contract%2C%20we%20have%20laid%20the%20foundations%20of%20India's%20long-term%20involvement%20at%20Chabahar%2C%26quot%3B%20Union%20Minister%20Sonowal%20said%20on%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chabahar%20port%20is%20being%20projected%20as%20a%20key%20hub%20for%20the%20International%20North-South%20Transport%20Corridor%20project%20--%20a%207%2C200-km-long%20multimode%20transport%20project%20for%20moving%20freight%20between%20India%2C%20Iran%2C%20Afghanistan%2C%20Armenia%2C%20Azerbaijan%2C%20Russia%2C%20Central%20Asia%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscussions%20on%20developing%20Chabahar%20Port%20were%20first%20held%20in%202003%20during%20then%20Iranian%20President%20Muhammad%20Khatami's%20visit%20to%20India.%20In%202013%2C%20India%20committed%20to%20investing%20%24100%20million%20towards%20its%20development.%20A%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20to%20develop%20the%20port%20was%20signed%20in%20May%202015.%20The%20contract%20was%20executed%20in%202016%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20trip%20to%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kandla%20port%20in%20Gujarat%20is%20the%20closest%20to%20Chabahar%20port%20at%20550%20Nautical%20Miles.%20The%20distance%20between%20Chabahar%20and%20Mumbai%20is%20786%20Nautical%20Miles.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715660220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmdp2b8g_chabahar-port-_625x300_14_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchabahar-port-india-us-ties-anyone-considering-on-indias-chabahar-pact-with-iran-a-us-warning-5658630%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shortly%20after%20India%20signed%20a%2010-year%20contract%20to%20operate%20Iran's%20Chabahar%20port%2C%20the%20US%20has%20warned%20that%20its%20sanctions%20on%20Tehran%20remain%20in%20place%20and%20anyone%20considering%20business%20deals%20with%20them%20needs%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Baware%20of%20the%20potential%20risk%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchabahar-port-in