en%20people%20died%20and%20over%2070%20were%20injured%20when%20a%20massive%20billboard%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fvideo-7-injured-some-feared-trapped-after-mumbai-dust-storm-uproots-billboard-5653884%5C%22%3Ecollapsed%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20a%20fierce%20storm%20that%20battered%20Mumbai%20Monday%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20100-foot%20billboard%2C%20situated%20opposite%20a%20fuel%20station%20in%20the%20Ghatkopar%20area%20of%20Mumbai%2C%20succumbed%20to%20the%20ferocity%20of%20the%20storm%2C%20crashing%20down%20with%20alarming%20force%2C%20directly%20onto%20the%20fuel%20station%20below.%20CCTV%20footage%20from%20the%20area%20captured%20the%20metal%20structure%20tearing%20through%20the%20roofs%20of%20several%20cars%20before%20thudding%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESearch%20and%20rescue%20mission%20is%20currently%20in%20progress.%20The%20NDRF%20has%20dispatched%20two%20teams%20to%20assist%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Mumbai%20Fire%20Brigade%20and%20other%20involved%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVideo%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fvideo-huge-scaffolding-ripped-apart-by-dust-storm-in-mumbai-5654541%5C%22%3EHuge%20Scaffolding%20Ripped%20Apart%20By%20Dust%20Storm%20In%20Mumbai%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hoarding%20was%20erected%20by%20Ego%20Media%20on%20a%20plot%20which%20has%20been%20leased%20to%20the%20Police%20Welfare%20Corporation%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20government's%20Police%20Housing%20Division.%20There%20are%20four%20hoardings%20from%20Ego%20Media%20on%20the%20premises%2C%20one%20of%20which%20collapsed%20Monday%20evening.%20Mumbai%20Police%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20the%20owner%20of%20Ego%20Media%2C%20along%20with%20others%20implicated%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Ego%20Media%20was%20granted%20permission%20for%20all%20four%20hoardings%2C%20including%20the%20one%20that%20fell%2C%20by%20the%20Assistant%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Railways)%2C%20no%20authorisation%20or%20No%20Objection%20Certificate%20(NOC)%20was%20obtained%20from%20the%20BMC%20before%20installation.%20Consequently%2C%20the%20BMC%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20Railway%20Police's%20ACP%20and%20the%20Railway%20Commissioner%2C%20demanding%20the%20cancellation%20of%20all%20permissions%20granted%20by%20the%20Railways%20and%20the%20removal%20of%20the%20hoardings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Pics%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fmumbai-news%2Fin-pics-mumbai-sky-turns-murky-after-massive-dust-storm-rainfall-5653797%5C%22%3EMumbai%20Sky%20Turns%20Murky%20After%20Massive%20Dust%20Storm%2C%20Rainfall%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMumbai%20last%20evening%20found%20itself%20besieged%20by%20a%20sudden%20and%20powerful%20dust%20storm%20which%20enveloped%20the%20metropolis%20in%20darkness%2C%20with%20residents%20taking%20to%20social%20media%20to%20share%20accounts%20of%20the%20unfolding%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransport%20networks%20bore%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20storm's%20fury%2C%20with%20local%20trains%20and%20airport%20services%20grinding%20to%20a%20halt%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20storm.%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20International%20Airport%20(CSMIA)%20was%20compelled%20to%20suspend%20flight%20operations%20temporarily%2C%20citing%20low%20visibility%20and%20gusty%20winds%20as%20the%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20issued%20urgent%20warnings%2C%20forecasting%20thunderstorms%20accompanied%20by%20lightning%20and%20heavy%20rain%20for%20Mumbai%20and%20surrounding%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20unseasonal%20rain%20offered%20some%20respite%20from%20the%20sweltering%20heat%2C%20power%20outages%20in%20various%20districts%2C%20including%20Thane's%20Kalwa%2C%20added%20further%20hardships%20for%20residents%20already%20grappling%20with%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20storm.%20Uprooted%20trees%20and%20structural%20damage%20were%20also%20reported%20from%20satellite%20towns%20such%20as%20Thane%2C%20Ambernath%2C%20Badlapur%2C%20Kalyan%2C%20and%20Ulhasnagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20visited%20the%20site%20of%20the%20collapse%20and%20assured%20that%20his%20government%20would%20conduct%20a%20structural%20audit%20of%20all%20hoardings%20in%20the%20city.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hoardings%2C%20if%20found%20illegal%20and%20dangerous%2C%20would%20be%20removed%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20very%20unfortunate%20incident.%20The%20government%20will%20probe%20it%2C%20and%20the%20people%20responsible%20will%20face%20action.%20I%20have%20also%20asked%20the%20BMC%20commissioner%20to%20conduct%20a%20structural%20audit%20of%20all%20the%20hoardings%20in%20the%20city.%20Those%20found%20illegal%20and%20dangerous%20will%20be%20removed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Minister%20also%20announced%20an%20aid%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20to%20the%20families%20of%20each%20person%20killed%20in%20the%20hoarding%20collapse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715654340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F9vfolru8_mumbai-hoarding-collapse-ani-_625x300_14_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-hoarding-collapse-deaths-rise-to-14-police-case-against-ad-agency-5658087%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fourteen%20people%20died%20and%20over%2070%20were%20injured%20when%20a%20massive%20billboard%20collapsed%20during%20a%20fierce%20storm%20that%20battered%20Mumbai%20Monday%20evening.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-hoarding-collapse-deaths-rise-to-14-police-case-against-ad-agency-5658087%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmumbai-hoar