0bringing%20back%20mandatory%20military%20service%20for%20young%20people.%20This%20comes%20as%20Germany%20looks%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20soldiers%20in%20its%20military%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Metro%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20German%20military%20is%20currently%20grappling%20with%20a%20deficit%20of%2021%2C000%20soldiers%2C%20a%20gap%20it%20needs%20to%20bridge%20to%20meet%20NATO%20defence%20plans.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20officials%20are%20deliberating%20over%20three%20potential%20solutions%2C%20with%20a%20decision%20expected%20to%20be%20announced%20by%20Pistorius%20as%20early%20as%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2024%2F05%2F13%2Fteenagers-germany-conscripted-russia-war-fears-20826329%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Metro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%2C%20The%20first%20option%20on%20the%20table%20is%20a%20compulsory%20year%20of%20military%20service%20for%20all%20young%20adults%20upon%20turning%2018.%20The%20second%20proposal%20involves%20mandatory%20enlistment%20forms%20and%20testing%20for%20all%2018-year-old%20males%2C%20with%20a%20sufficient%20number%20of%20suitable%20candidates%20being%20enlisted%20to%20fill%20the%20recruitment%20gap.%20In%20this%20scenario%2C%20females%20would%20have%20the%20choice%20to%20opt-in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20and%20final%20option%20does%20not%20involve%20compulsory%20service.%20Instead%2C%20all%20school%20leavers%20would%20be%20sent%20an%20enlistment%20form%2C%20which%20they%20could%20choose%20to%20complete%20voluntarily.%20A%20decision%20on%20which%20option%20to%20implement%20is%20expected%20next%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20a%20recent%20visit%20to%20the%20US%2C%20Mr%20Pistorius%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20some%20form%20of%20conscription%20in%20Germany.%20He%20believes%20it%20was%20a%20mistake%20to%20end%20military%20service%2C%20which%20used%20to%20require%2018-year-old%20boys%20to%20serve%20for%20a%20year.%20His%20views%20are%20supported%20by%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%2C%20the%20conservative%20Christian%20Democratic%20Union%20(CDU).%20Concerns%20have%20heightened%20across%20Europe%20after%20Vladimir%20Putin%20announced%20putting%20nuclear%20forces%20on%20high%20alert%2C%20blaming%20the%20West%20for%20escalating%20conflicts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spokeswoman%20for%20Germany's%20defence%20ministry%20said%20last%20week%3A%20%26quot%3BWith%20the%20annexation%20of%20Crimea%20in%202014%20and%20the%20military%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20Russia%20demonstrated%20its%20willingness%20to%20use%20force%20to%20change%20borders%20in%20Europe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715654220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F48a3i6ho_german-military_625x300_14_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fis-history-repeating-germany-debates-return-of-compulsory-military-service-5658197%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20bid%20to%20strengthen%20its%20military%20forces%2C%20Germany%20is%20considering%20the%20reintroduction%20of%20mandatory%20military%20service%20for%20its%20youth.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fis-history-repeating-germany-debates-return-of-compulsory-military-service-5658197%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fis-history-repeating-germany-debates-return-of-compulsory-military-service-5658197%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fis-history-repeating-germany-debates-return-of-compulsory-military-service-5658197%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe%20Are%20Not%20An%20African%20Country%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-Pak%20Board%20Chief's%20Startling%20Remark%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20star%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ramiz%20Raja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41527-rameez-raja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERamiz%20Raja%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20extremely%20displeased%20with%20the%20coverage%20of%20the%20ongoing%20T20I%20series%20between%20Pakistan%20and%20Ireland.%20Ireland%20won%20the%20first%20T20I%20but%20Pakistan%20bounced%20back%20to%20win%20the%20second%20match%20in%20the%20series%20that%20is%20the%20start%20of%20their%20beginning%20for%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024.%20Pakistan%20will%20next%20take%20on%20England%20in%20a%20four%20T20I%20series.%20Raja%20said%20that%20the%20lack%20of%20DRS%20and%20replays%20is%20not%20befitting%20of%20a%20match%20featuring%20Pakistan%20and%20added%20that%20he%20was%20not%20able%20to%20follow%20the%20action%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20thing%20which%20I%20don't%20like%20at%20all%20is%20the%20coverage%20of%20this%20match.%20It%20feels%20like%20a%20club%20game%20is%20being%20telecast.%20Only%20two%20cameras%20are%20there.%20There's%20no%20DRS%2C%20no%20replays%2C%20you%20don't%20get%20an%20idea%20of%20the%20boundary%20rope%2C%20you%20can't%20enjoy%20a%20good%20shot%20being%20played%20or%20good%20balls%20being%20bowled.%20This%20is%20extremely%20unfair%20to%20the%20Pakistan%20cricket%20product.%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20love%20Pakistan%20cricket.%20It%20has%20an%20aura%20around%20the%20world.%20And%20to%20present%20it%20like%20this%20is%20unfair%20to%20Pakistan%20cricket%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20on%20YouTube.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20should%20have%20looked%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSomeone%20should%20have%20figured%20it%20out%20earlier.%20If%20the%20coverage%20was%20going%20to%20be%20like%20this%2C%20whichever%20broadcasting%20company%20it%20was%2C%20should%20have%20taken%20the%20rights%20from%20Cricket%20Ireland.%20I%20know%20they%20have%20the%20rights%2C%20but%20it%20should%20have%20been%20taken%20away%20and%20the%20coverage%20should%20have%20been%20made%20much%20better%20for%20this%20series%20because%20this%20marks%20the%20beginning%20of%20our%20road%20to%20the%20World%20Cup.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20tell%20you%20this%20with%20certainty%20if%20India%20knew%20this%20situation%2C%20they%20would%20never%20have%20allowed%20such%20coverage.%20Because%20your%20honour%20is%20in%20your%20hands.%20So%20Pakistan's%20honour%20should%20also%20be%20in%20their%20hands.%20Through%20coverage%20like%20this%2C%20our%20cricket%20looks%20flat.%20And%20it%20is%20unfair%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaja%20further%20said%20that%20the%20coverage%20was%20'unfair'%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20compared%20it%20to%20the%20broadcast%20quality%20of%20matches%20featuring%20African%20teams.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20an%20African%20country%20that%20the%20coverage%20for%20our%20games%20can%20be%20this%20poor.%20This%20series%20is%20not%20telecast%20in%20England.%20It's%20not%20available%20on%20Sky.%20Primarily%20because%20it%20is%20being%20covered%20like%20this.%20This%20is%20unfair%20to%20Pakistan%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20former%20Pakistan%20cricket%20team%20star%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715654160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fuv68jopo_ramiz-raja_625x300_04_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fwe-are-not-an-african-country-ex-pcb-chiefs-startling-remark-on-ireland-vs-pakistan-series-5656800%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ramiz%20Raja%20was%20extremely%20critical%20of%20the%20coverage%20of%20the%20ongoing%20T20I%20series%20between%20Pakistan%20and%20Ireland.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blinken%20in%20Ukraine%20as%20US%20weapons%20reach%20front%20line%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715653891000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2