%20be%20responsible%20for%20defining%20their%20roles%2C%20their%20performance%20and%20ongoing%20development.%20The%20Head%20Coach%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20reviewing%2C%20maintaining%2C%20and%20enforcing%20the%20disciplinary%20codes%20within%20the%20Indian%20Men's%20team.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20required%20%26quot%3Bqualifications%2C%20experience%2C%20knowledge%20and%20skills%26quot%3B%20are%20also%20interesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShould%20have%20played%20minimum%20of%2030%20Test%20Matches%20or%2050%20ODI's%3B%20or%20Head%20Coach%20of%20a%20full%20member%20Test%20Playing%20Nation%2C%20for%20a%20minimum%20period%20of%202%20years%3B%20or%20Head%20Coach%20of%20an%20Associate%20member%20%2FIPL%20Team%20or%20Equivalent%20International%20League%2FFirst%20Class%20Teams%2F%20National%20A%20teams%2C%20for%20a%20minimum%20period%20of%203%20years%3B%20or%20Should%20have%20BCCI%20Level%203%20Certification%20or%20equivalent%3B%20and%20Should%20be%20below%2060%20years%20of%20age%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BCCI%20release%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20remuneration%2C%20the%20BCCI%20says%20its%20%26quot%3Bnegotiable%20and%20will%20be%20commensurated%20with%20experience.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'operating%20environment'%20column%20is%20also%20interesting.%20It%20reads%3A%20%26quot%3BMust%20be%20willing%20to%20meet%20work%20expectations%20and%20pressures%20associated%20with%20handling%20marquee%20athletes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715652900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ftviogaj8_rahul-dravid-rohit-sharma-x_625x300_09_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fshould-be-below-60-remuneration-bccis-criteria-for-new-team-india-head-coach-job-5656720%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20tenure%20of%20the%20current%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20head%20coach%20Rahul%20Dravid%20ends%20with%20the%20T20%20World%202024%2C%20which%20runs%20till%20June-end%22%2C%22author