econnect%20with%20old%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPassaro%20wasn't%20going%20to%20make%20the%20trip%20from%20Florida.%20His%20wife%20and%2037-year-old%20son%2C%20John%2C%20had%20recently%20died%2C%20both%20within%2010%20months%20of%20each%20other%2C%20according%20to%20TODAY.com.%20His%20family%20talked%20him%20into%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f0e446de-6509-4da8-b41a-13665014a86d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20instant%20attraction%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Passaro%20and%20Hall%2C%20their%20reunion%20was%20electric.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20an%20attraction%20between%20us%20that%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20told%20The%20Washington%20Post.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20went%20over%20to%20say%20goodbye%2C%20he%20leaned%20over%20and%20gave%20me%20a%20kiss.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%2C%20Passaro%20mailed%20Hall%20a%20handwritten%20letter.%20After%20reading%20it%2C%20she%20called%20him%20and%20they%20spoke%20on%20the%20phone%20for%20six%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20and%20again%2C%20and%20again%20for%20the%20next%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Hall%20visited%20Passaro%20in%20Miami.%20On%20her%20second%20visit%20during%20Christmas%20that%20year%2C%20they%20decided%20she'd%20move%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20lives%20blended%20together%20beautifully.%20Passaro%20described%20them%20both%20as%20%26quot%3Bfamily-oriented%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdevoted%26quot%3B%20to%20their%20kids%2C%20grandkids%2C%20and%20great-grandkids%20in%20The%20Post.%20They%20also%20love%20traveling%2C%20going%20out%20to%20dinner%20and%20art%20shows%2C%20and%20golfing.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20so%20adorable%20at%20the%20golf%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20James%2C%20one%20of%20Passaro's%20sons%2C%20told%20The%20Washington%20Post.%20%26quot%3BHe%20hits%20the%20ball%2C%20and%20she%20tells%20him%20which%20way%20it%20went%20because%20he%20can't%20see%20very%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22674ad800-b108-47b1-881d-dd1ff568426c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHall%20finally%20got%20a%20real%20wedding%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20lived%20together%20for%2020%20years%20when%2C%20last%20October%2C%20Hall%20%26quot%3Bwondered%20out%20loud%26quot%3B%20why%20they%20hadn't%20gotten%20married%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Post.%20With%20tears%20in%20their%20eyes%2C%20they%20agreed%20to%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20and%20her%20daughters%20went%20to%20six%20boutiques%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20a%20gown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20kept%20saying%20at%2088%2C%20maybe%20I%20shouldn't%20wear%20a%20veil%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20told%20TODAY.com.%20%26quot%3BMy%20daughters%20said%2C%20'Mom%2C%20quit%20trying%20not%20to%20look%20like%20a%20bride.%20You're%20a%20bride.%20We're%20going%20to%20do%20the%20whole%20thing.'%20When%20I%20got%20up%20there%20to%20him%2C%20he%20said%20to%20me%2C%20'You%20look%20so%20beautiful.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Grand%20Haven%20Amenities%20in%20Palm%20Coast%2C%20Florida%2C%20their%20sons%20and%20daughters%20walked%20them%20down%20the%20aisle.%20Two%20great-granddaughters%20were%20flower%20girls%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20their%20first%20dance%2C%20the%20couple%20jitterbugged%20to%20%26quot%3BKansas%20City%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20hit%20song%20from%20the%201950s%20that%20they%20danced%20to%20as%20teenagers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20feel%20the%20same%20way%20as%20I%20did%20at%2015%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20told%20TODAY.com.%20%26quot%3BI%20still%20get%20the%20butterflies.%20I%20just%20love%20him%20so%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-school-crushes-married-at-88-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715637587000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F664253a29686a6f37bff626f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigh-school-crushes-married-at-88-2024-5%22%2C%2