o%20a%20host%20of%20other%20plant%20species%20that%20are%20in%20the%20IUCN%20(International%20Union%20for%20Conservation%20of%20Nature)%20red%20list%20and%20classified%20as%20%E2%80%98threatened%E2%80%99%20by%20Uttarakhand%20board.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20has%20been%20working%20closely%20to%20conserve%20plant%20habitats%20and%20protect%20them%20from%20illegal%20trade.%20They%20are%20also%20innovating%20ways%20to%20grow%20them%20in%20their%20natural%20habitats%20and%20in%20their%20research%20centres%20as%20well.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20scale%20these%20plant%20populations%20at%20their%20original%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IFS%20Officer%20Sanjeev%20Chaturvedi%20has%20dedicated%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20to%20conserving%20endemic%20plant%20species%20in%20Nainital%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349420%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIFS%20Officer%20Sanjeev%20Chaturvedi%20has%20dedicated%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20to%20conserving%20endemic%20plant%20species%20in%20Nainital%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Chaturve