%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20identify%20the%20plants%20based%20on%20their%20family%20and%20genus%2C%20then%20proceed%20to%20collect%20their%20specimens.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20some%20factors%20play%20spoilsport%20to%20this%20%E2%80%94%20illegal%20trade%2C%20growth%20of%20invasive%20species%2C%20and%20wildlife%20feasting%20on%20the%20fallen%20fruits%20and%20seeds.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20the%20birds%20eat%20these%20seeds%20and%20fruits%2C%20it%20disturbs%20the%20natural%20regeneration%20of%20the%20plant.%20There%20is%20no%20chance%20of%20a%20new%20crop.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20and%20Chaturvedi%20lead%20the%20team%20to%20collect%20these%20fruits%20and%20seeds%20and%20take%20them%20back%20to%20the%20centre%20where%20they%20conduct%20experiments%20to%20cultivate%20these%20plants%20through%20vegetative%20propagation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20terrain%2C%20weather%20and%20climate%20are%20challenging%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20points%20out.%20%E2%80%9CEspecially%20when%2C%20after%20restoration%2C%20we%20proceed%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F273494%2Fabdul-kareem-inspiring-hero-who-grew-a-forest-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erehabilitate%20the%20plants%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20in%20their%20natural%20environments.%20While%20these%20altitudes%20are%20conducive%20for%20their%20growth%2C%20it%20is%20a%20tough%20terrain%20for%20us%20to%20access.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChaturvedi%20adds%20that%20they%20zero%20in%20on%20the%20plant%20species%20after%20thorough%20research%20through%20Vedic%20literature%20as%20well%20as%20the%20IUCN%20lists.%20Once%20they%20demarcate%20the%20areas%20where%20the%20plants%20thrive%20%E2%80%94%20taking%20care%20not%20to%20publicise%20it%20too%20much%20%E2%80%94%20they%20take%20the%20GPS%20coordinates%20of%20the%20place%20and%20in%20the%20months%20that%20follow%2C%20conduct%20studies%20on%20the%20pla