%20of%20the%20few%20species%20that%20can%20survive%20in%20frost%20and%20snow%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Chaturvedi%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20his%20term%20in%20the%20forests%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Chaturvedi%20has%20also%20been%20instrumental%20in%20developing%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20moss%20garden%20in%20Nainital%20which%20boasts%20around%2090%20different%20types%20of%20moss%20species%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F248029%2Fwoman-entrepreneur-pathanamthitta-kerala-moss-rose-cinderella-jumbo-table-rose-covid-19-pandemic-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen-air%20fernery%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Ranikhet%20with%20200%20different%20types%20of%20ferns%20and%20a%20grass%20conservatory%20in%20Ranikhet%20with%20more%20than%20100%20grass%20species.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20always%20underestimate%20the%20importance%20of%20grasses%2C%20but%20the%20latest%20research%20shows%20them%20to%20be%20more%20effective%20in%20carbon%20sequestration%20than%20trees%20because%20they%20store%20carbon%20in%20their%20roots%20instead%20of%20releasing%20it%20into%20the%20atmosphere.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Chaturvedi%20shies%20away%20from%20accepting%20applause.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20says%2C%20if%20there%20is%20anyone%20that%20deserves%20the%20praise%20it%20is%20Mother%20Nature.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20huge%20respect%20for%20her.%20She%20has%20designed%20each%20and%20everything%20in%20such%20a%20connected%20manner%3B%20every%20moss%2C%20every%20lichen%2C%20every%20insect%2C%20every%20pollinator.%20They%20are%20all%20so%20beautifully%20interconnected%20with%20each%20other%20that%20if%20you%20take%20out%20even%20one%20string%2C%20the%20entire%20chain%20will%20be%20disturbed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1715610366000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fplant-conservation-1715249611.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D349417%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IFS%20officer%20Sanjeev%20Chaturvedi%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20save%20and%20foster%20Uttarakhand's%20miracle%20plants%20like%20Patwa%2C%20Himalayan%20Lily%20and%20Gentiana%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F349417%2Fifs-officer-sanjeev-chaturvedi-uttarakhand-endangered-plants-conservation-patwa-gentiana-lilium-polyphyllum%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98How%20I%20Got%20a%20Job%20At%20NASA%E2%80%99%3A%20Aerospace%20Engineer%20Shares%205%20Tips%20to%20Build%20a%20Career%20in%20Space%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAkshata%20Krishnamurthy%E2%80%99s%20fascination%20with%20space%20began%20as%20a%20child%20as%20she%20wondered%20about%20what%20lies%20beyond%20our%20planet.%20Her%20curiosity%20was%20fuelled%20by%20weekly%20visits%20to%20the%20planetariums%20and%20air%20shows%20in%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20no%20surprise%20then%20that%20this%20young%20girl%20would%20want%20to%20pursue%20a%20career%20in%20aerospace.%20But%20how%2C%20where%2C%20and%20what%20to%20do%20to%20achieve%20this%20dream%20was%20a%20path%20she%20had%20to%20navigate%20on%20her%20own.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20incredible%20talent%20and%20a%20dogged%20pursuit%20of%20her%20goal%2C%20she%20became%20a%20student%20at%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(MIT)%2C%20which%20was%20a%20huge%20deal%20for%20the%20student%20who%20studied%20in%20a%20state%20board%20school%20and%20came%20from%20a%20middle%20class%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20this%20gritty%20woman%20works%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324699%2Fawais-ahmed-founded-space-startup-pixxel-hyperspectral-satellite-launch-hyperloop-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaerospace%20engineer%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20National%20Aeronautics%20and%20Space%20Administration%20(NASA).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20her%20journey%20was%20not%20an%20easy%20one.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavigating%20through%20the%20various%20hurdles%20of%20having%20an%20education%20abroad%20to%20setting%20foot%20at%20NASA%20as%20a%20full-time%20employee%20took%20her%20almost%2015%20years.%20But%20this%2035-year-old%20is%20making%20it%20easy%20for%20others%20by%20sharing%20her%20experiences%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20mentoring%20them.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20her%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EIn%20pursuit%20of%20the%20universe%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkshata%20works%20as%20a%20Principal%20Investigator%20and%20Space%20Systems%20Engineer%20at%20NASA%20Jet%20Propulsion%20Laboratory%20(JPL)%20on%20two%20space%20missions.%20She%20is%20the%20mission%20science%20phase%20lead%20on%20the%20NASA-ISRO%20Synthetic%20Aperture%20Radar%20mission%20(NISAR)%20and%20robotics%20systems%20engineer%20on%20the%20MARS%202020%20Perseverance%20rover%2C%20operating%20the%20rover%20on%20MARS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20lifelong%20tryst%20with%20space%20took%20roots%20at%20an%20airshow%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%202003.%20It%20was%20the%20Aero%20India%20show%20at%20the%20Yelahanka%20air%20force%20base%20that%20perhaps%20started%20it%20all.%20The%20aerobatic%20manoeuvres%20of%20the%20Sukhoi%20Su-30%20pilots%20left%20the%20youngster%20captivated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FFwPOzvr0oxQ%3Ffeature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%