ry%20(JPL)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20India%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20human%20space%20programme.%20You%20either%20became%20a%20cosmonaut%20with%20Russia%20or%20you%20became%20an%20astronaut%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F295003%2Futtarakhand-scientist-amit-pandey-in-nasa-artemis-moon-rocket-mission%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20space%20programme.%3C%2Fa%3E%20There%20were%20no%20Indians%20who%20weren%E2%80%99t%20US%20citizens%20in%20the%20programme%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Akshata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20soon%20discovered%20that%20a%20large%20percentage%20of%20astronauts%20had%20actually%20studied%20at%20MIT.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9CSince%20then%2C%20I%20knew%20that%20I%20had%20to%20study%20at%20MIT%20as%20I%20felt%20that%20it%20would%20provide%20me%20with%20a%20good%20chance%20to%20go%20to%20space.%20MIT%20has%20actually%20sent%2044%20astronauts%20to%20space%20and%20most%20of%20them%20pursued%20their%20PhDs%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20gave%20the%20young%20schoolgirl%20a%20clear%20path%20to%20focus%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20became%20the%20only%20female%20student%20in%20her%20mechanical%20engineering%20stream%20at%20RV%20College%20of%20Engineering%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20graduating%20in%202010.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%2C%20she%20got%20a%20full%20ride%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20in%20Urbana-Champaign%20to%20pursue%20a%20masters%20in%20aerospace%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20challenge%20before%20Akshata%20presented%20itself%20in%20the%20form%20of%20getting%20an%20aerospace%20job%20in%20the%20US%20without%20a%20citizenship%20or%20a%20green%20card.%20To%20be%20accepted%20as%20a%20doctoral%20candidate%20at%20MIT%2C%20she%20would%20need%20some%20work%20experience%2C%20she%20learned.%C2%A0%