esting%20during%20the%20construction%20of%20their%202%2C000%20sq%20ft%20home%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20learnt%20that%20even%20borewells%20as%20deep%20as%201%2C000%20feet%20in%20our%20locality%20went%20dry%20over%20time.%20This%20was%20the%20reason%20we%20chose%20not%20to%20drill%20a%20borewell.%20Besides%2C%20we%20still%20depend%20on%20water%20tankers%20as%20the%20Cauvery%20water%20supply%20is%20insufficient.%20This%20dependency%20increases%20during%20summer%20with%20the%20Cauvery%20water%20supply%20reducing%20to%20one-fourth%20of%20its%20usual%20quantity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohit%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20harvest%20rainwater%20for%20non-potable%20purposes%20like%20cleaning%2C%20bathing%2C%20and%20gardening%20needs%2C%20except%20for%20drinking%20and%20cooking.%20This%20ensures%20they%20are%20unaffected%20by%20the%20depleting%20groundwater%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERainwater%20meets%20half%20of%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20annual%20water%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CEvery%20monsoon%2C%20we%20save%20up%20to%2035%2C000%20litres%20of%20rainwater.%20We%20use%20the%20harvested%20rainwater%20for%20cleaning%20and%20gardening%20purposes.%20Whereas%2C%20we%20use%20the%20Cauvery%20water%20once%20a%20week%20and%20tanker%20supply%20thrice%20a%20month%20for%20kitchen%2C%20bathing%2C%20dishes%2C%20and%20laundry%20purposes%2C%20and%20water%20cans%20for%20drinking%20needs.%20We%20are%20a%20family%20of%20four%20and%20rainwater%20takes%20care%20of%20half%20of%20our%20annual%20water%20needs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaintaining%20garden%20with%20350%20plants%20amid%20water%20crisis%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECloser%20to%20their%20rainwater%20harvesting%20tank%2C%20the%20couple%20has%20maintained%20a%20lush%20green%20garden%20of%20350%20plants%20comprising%20ornamental%2C%20flowering%2C%20succulents%2C%20handfuls%20of%20greens%2C%20her