0psychometric%20tests%20to%20discover%20their%20career%20inclinations%2C%20guiding%20their%20subject%20choices%20when%20they%20enter%20Class%208.%20This%20personalised%20method%20ensures%20their%20interests%20and%20strengths%20are%20considered.%20Alongside%20languages%20and%20math%2C%20students%20explore%20diverse%20subjects%20through%20practical%20experiences%20and%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20recently%2C%20the%20students%20completed%20a%20board%20game%20project%20where%20they%20designed%20and%20created%20their%20own%20board%20games%2C%20complete%20with%20unique%20rules.%20Students%20are%20encouraged%20to%20delve%20deeply%20into%20subjects%20of%20their%20choosing%20and%20conduct%20in-depth%20studies%20according%20to%20their%20interests%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20organisation%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20children's%20education%2C%20food%2C%20clothing%20and%20shelter.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fpathshala-2-1715240423-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-349409%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20organisation%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20education%2C%20foo