2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20the%20unique%20concept%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20month%2C%20we%20treat%2034%2C578%20patients%20in%20total%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Alam%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20shying%20away%20from%20taking%20credit%20for%20this%20massive%20volume.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20four%20boats%20in%20total%20and%20the%20schedule%20for%20each%20is%20set%20every%20Monday.%20Throughout%20the%20week%2C%20we%20travel%20across%20the%2030%20islands%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%2C%20covering%20six%20blocks%20in%20the%20North%20and%2013%20in%20the%20South.%20On%20Sundays%2C%20we%20return%20to%20the%20mainland%20where%20we%20stock%20up%20on%20supplies%2C%20medicines%2C%20rest%20and%20recharge%20for%20the%20next%20week.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Alam%20has%20been%20doing%20this%20for%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20In%20fact%2C%20he%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20doctors%20to%20be%20appointed%20by%20the%20couple%20Mohammed%20Abdul%20Wohab%20and%20Sabitri%20Pal%20%E2%80%94%20the%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20SHIS%20Foundation%20(Southern%20Health%20Improvement%20Samity)%20started%20in%201980%20%E2%80%94%20when%20Wohab%2C%20a%20lawyer%2C%20and%20Pal%2C%20a%20teacher%2C%20bonded%20over%20their%20intentions%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F278313%2Fsundarbans-hingalganj-island-english-medium-school-inspiring-teacher-kolkata%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echampion%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98People%20were%20dying%20in%20front%20of%20my%20eyes%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E380%20mm%20of%20rainfall%20in%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20forget%2027%20September%201978.%20Thousands%20died%2C%20starved%20and%20were%20left%20homeless%20as%20the%20torrential%20rain%20washed%20away%20entire%20houses.%20Wohab%2C%20who%20lived%20in%20Howrah%20at%20the%20time%2C%20recalls%20the%20harrowing%20ordeal.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20heartbreaking%20to%20watch%20people%20and%20their%20cattle%20drowning%20in%20the%20water.%20All%20around%2C%20flood%20victims%20were%20taking%20shelter%20in%20other%E2%80%99s%20homes%20and%20schools%2C%20and%20even%20climbing%20up%20trees%20to%20avoid%20drowning.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20one%20knew%20what%20the%20next%20week%2C%20much%20less%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20would%20bring.%20It%20was%20in%20this%20chaos%20that%20Wohab%20watched%20as%20a%20man%2C%20who%20seemed%20like%20a%20foreigner%2C%20was%20rowing%20his%20boat%20through%20the%20floodwater%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329667%2Fpalghar-kiran-kamdar-free-homemade-khichdi-for-patients-hospital-parkinson-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistributing%20food%20packets%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20people.%20This%20attracted%20the%20lawyer%20who%20was%20working%20as%20secretary%20to%20a%20village-level%20governing%20body%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-10.31.59-AM-1714724688.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20boat%20clinics%20are%20equipped%20with%20all%20essential%20medical%20equipment%20and%20medicines%20needed%20to%20help%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-10.31.59-AM-1714724688.jpeg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-10.31.59-AM-1714724688-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-10.31.59-AM-1714724688-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-10.31.59-AM-1714724688-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-10.31.59-AM-1714724688-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348886%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20boat%20clinics%20are%20equipped%20with%20all%20essential%20medical%20equipment%20and%20medicines%20needed%20to%20help%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wohab%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.04.48-PM-1714724848.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Patients%20across%2030%20islands%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%20are%20treated%20by%20the%20doctors%20onboard%20the%20boat%20clinic%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.04.48-PM-1714724848.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.04.48-PM-1714724848-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.04.48-PM-1714724848-500x282.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.04.48-PM-1714724848-768x433.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-22-at-12.04.48-PM-1714724848-150x85.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-348887%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22722%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPatients%20across%2030%20islands%20of%20the%20Sundarbans%20are%20treated%20by%20the%20doctors%20onboard%20the%20boat%20clinic%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wohab%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20would%20soon%20learn%2C%20the%20man%20was%20Grandjean%20Gaston%2C%20a%20nurse%20from%20Switzerland.%20%E2%80%9CBrother%20Gaston%20had%20been%20battling%20a%20heart%20condition%20and%20had%20decided%20to%20dedicate%20his%20life%20to%20the%20poor%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wohab%20explains.%20He%20wanted%20to%20follow%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20that%20year%2C%20inspired%20by%20Gaston%E2%80%99s%20story%2C%20the%20couple%20decided%20to%20recalibrate%20their%20plans%3B%20and%20moved%20back%20to%20their%20hometown%20in%20Bhangar%2C%20South%2024%20Parganas.%20The%20goal%20of%20this%20move%20was%20simple%3A%20Spot%20areas%20where%20their%20communities%20lacked%20resources%20and%20bridge%20those%20gaps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20flood%20waters%20began%20to%20recede%2C%20they%20left%20behind%20many%20challenges%20for%20the%20residents%20of%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20chill%20in%20the%20air%20and%20the%20bacteria%20breeding%20in%20the%20murky%20waters%20had%20only%20added%20to%20the%20existing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331526%2Fpune-startup-innovates-ai-based-technology-screen-tuberculosis-within-seconds-innovation-in-healthcare%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebattle%20against%20tuberculosis%3C%2Fa%3E%20(TB)%20that%20the%20community%20was%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20were%20dying%20in%20front%20of%20our%20eyes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wohab%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20often%20started%20with%20a%20cough%20and%20before%20the%20person%20knew%20it%2C%20they%20were%20detected%20with%20TB.%20As%20we%20spoke%20to%20people%20in%20the%20neighbourhood%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20almost%2050%20percent%20of%20people%20with%20chest%20problems%20did%20not%20go%20for%20a%20checkup%20until%20they%20started%20vomiting%20blood.%20And%20once%20they%20reached%20this%20stage%2C%20it%20was%2C%20more%20often%20than%20not%2C%20too%20late.%20We%20also%20found%20that%20there%20were%20only%20three%20doctors%20in%20the%20Sundarbans%20at%20that%20time%20and%20more%20than%20three%20lakh%20patients.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20wanted%20to%20help.%20They%20had%20heard%20about%20doctors%20in%20Kolkata%20who%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F259846%2Fdoctors-couple-covid-relief-free-medicine-collection-underprivileged-shell%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistributing%20medicines%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20free.%20%E2%80%9CSabitri%20and%20I%20started%20making%20trips%20to%20these%20clinics%20to%20collect%20the%20medicine%20samples%20which%20we%20distributed%20in%20a%20small%20room%20that%20a%20tea%20shop%20owner%20had%20lent%20to%20us.%20Through%20the%20weeks%2C%20people%20from%20across%20Sundarban%20islands%20would%20come%20to%20get%20an%20antidote%20to%20tuberculosis%2C%20cold%2C%20cough%20and%20fever.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-23-at-10.53.09-AM-1714724989.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Abdul%20Wohab%20and%20Sabitri%20Pal%2C%20the%20founders%20of%20SHIS%20Foundation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-23-at-10.53.09-AM-1714724989.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-23-at-10.53.09-AM-1714724989-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-02-23-at-10.53.09-AM-1714724